The paper also discusses systems that contribute to the advancement of human and social intelligence, which suggests that it may also belong to categories such as cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper discusses the amplification of human intelligence, which could fall under categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
